<lyrics>[V1]
 1- msẖ lạqy klạm ạ̉qwlh whw wạqf ysmʿny
 lw lạqy wqwlthwlwạ hạtfrq fy ạ̹yh yʿny
 hạṣʿb ʿlyh yʿny
 yʿny klạmy mʿạh
 msẖ zy klạmy mʿ bạqy ạlnạs
 ạlly yʿml mtạ̉tẖr ʿlsẖạn ynthz frṣ wkẖlạṣ
 (yʿny ḥạss byạ wsạmʿ ṣwty
 bnạdy ʿlyh
 ṭb wlyh mạymdsẖ ạ̹ydh ysẖfyny
 ạ̉nạ mạṣʿbtsẖ ʿlyh)2
 hạysạmḥny ʿlsẖạn jrạ̉ty
 lkn dạ mn ʿsẖmy fyh
 jạyz tkwn ḥty̱ ṭryqty
 lkn mạlysẖ gẖyrk ạ̉nạdyh
 2- ʿạrf ṭbʿk ḥnyn yʿny ḥạss bjrạḥy
 ʿsẖạn jrḥy msẖ hyn dạ byzwd ạ̹lḥạḥy
 ạ̹ny ạ̉fhm bs ạ̹zạy ʿynk mạsẖftnysẖ
 yʿny ạ̹yh ạ̉ṣrkẖ yạ ạ̹lhy ạsẖfyny wlsh mạsẖftnysẖ</lyrics>
<title>msẖ lạqy̱ klạm</title>
